{"tid":1576044,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"10月1號送殯 有關衣着事宜","createTime":"2019-09-17T05:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T11:48:07.000Z","uid":281955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"df2ab108fce6bb7b20ab5df2cef9d8811bd07ce2","tid":1576044,"uid":281955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:21:58.000Z","msg":"最近媽媽嘅朋友有兩位親戚去世<br />\n一個喺香港出殯一個喺九龍出殯<br />\n一個係基督教徒另一個用道教義式<br />\n問我媽媽應該點着衫先啱<br />\n我媽媽話天主教同基督教一般都係着<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>全黑</strong></span></span><br />\n女士嘅話仲會戴<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑紗</span></span></strong><br />\n道教嘅話就一般披<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">麻戴孝着全白</span></span></strong>囉<br />\n媽媽話一般衣紙鋪頭都有孝服賣<br />\n殯儀館服務部都有<br />\n媽媽多口問幾時出殯呀<br />\n媽媽朋友就話都係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">10月1號</span></span></strong>囉好忙呀 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔知咁著我媽媽有無講錯呢？大家點睇？</span></strong>"},{"pid":"edbf4d4faf197a128f56df8fd2de33236b42f3d2","tid":1576044,"uid":281955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0K6hwB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0K6hwB2.jpg&h=9636db9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe3d56ec6b35edf8f3a00edc1c27a78b48ae27b7","tid":1576044,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:22:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/StbtyWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src